`server.js` — API + multi-household persistence + import/export/store normalization; **`module.exports = { normalizeStore, buildEntriesCsv }`** for tests; **`if (require.main === module)`** wraps listen + Discord reminder interval (so `npm test` does not bind a port or start the timer). Imports **`buildOpenApiDocument`** from **`lib/openapi-spec.cjs`**; **`GET /api/openapi.json`** is public (see **`requireApiAuth`** bypass list).
- `135` `normalizeEntry(row)` — entry shape, `choreId`, `locationIds`.
- `163` `normalizeChorePreset(row)` — validates title/points/color/scoringMode.
- `178` `normalizeChorePresets(arr)` — array normalization for presets.
- `188` `normalizeQuickChoreIds(ids, presets)` — validates quick bar ids against presets.
- `291` `normalizeStore(raw)` — canonicalizes store object read from disk (`discordWebhook`, `discordReminderSentAt`, **`pushSubscriptions`**, **`auditLog`**).
- `GET /api/audit` — recent audit events (auth required); **`appendAudit`** on entry/settings/scheduled/import/discord user actions.
- `451` `app.get('/api/entries', ...)` — list entries + `discordWebhook` for settings UI.
- Discord / Slack / generic webhooks + **Web Push (VAPID)**: `POST /api/discord-webhook/test`, `POST /api/discord-webhook/remind-now` (digest to webhooks and/or push); **`GET /api/push/vapid-public`**, **`GET/POST /api/push/subscriptions|subscribe|unsubscribe`**, **`POST /api/push/test`**; background timer sends overdue reminders per `discordReminderSentAt` to webhooks and/or registered push endpoints; **quiet hours** skip both; `discordWebhook` holds `quietHours*`, `slackWebhookUrl`, `genericWebhookUrl`; store **`pushSubscriptions`** (per household, max 24). Env **`CHORELOG_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY`**, **`CHORELOG_VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY`**, optional **`CHORELOG_VAPID_SUBJECT`**; `npm run vapid:keys` generates keys.
- `469`–`542` scheduled chore routes; `PUT /api/scheduled-chores/:id` supports title/interval/**startsOn**/**reminderEnabled** updates; `542` `POST .../complete` writes completion entry.
- `588` `app.put('/api/settings', ...)` — settings write (people/presets/quick ids/locations/**discordWebhook** with quiet hours + extra webhook URLs).
- `657` `app.post('/api/import', ...)` — import handler (replace/merge modes).
- `634` `app.get('/api/export', ...)` — export.
- `768` `app.post('/api/entries', ...)` — add entry (supports `choreId`, locations).
- `830` `app.put('/api/entries/:id', ...)` — update entry.

`index.html` — app shell, dialogs, script bootstrap.
- Settings: **Audit log** (`#auditLogList`, …); **Integrations** tab — **Discord reminders** + quiet hours + Slack/generic URLs (`#discordWebhookEnabled`, …, test / post-now) + **browser push** (`#btnPushSubscribe`, `#btnPushUnsubscribe`, `#btnPushTest`, `js/push-notifications.js`, **`sw.js`** `push` / `notificationclick`); **nav** (`#settingsNav`, tab panels).
- `62`–`74` **analytics filters** `#analyticsPersonFilter`, `#analyticsLocationFilter`, hint `#analyticsFilterHint`; then `analytics-stats-row` / `statsGrid`, `statsGridPoints`.
