- `entryMatchesLogSearch` — log-only text filter (whitespace AND tokens).
- `countsByPerson` / `pointsByPerson` / `taskCountsByDay` — use `entriesForAnalyticsMonth`.
- `fullRender()` — analytics filters, dual stat grids, bars, heatmap, log list, **scheduled log suggestion buttons** (`scheduledStatus` overdue/today/soon + `presetMatchingScheduledTitle`), dual MoM, scheduled dashboard.
