`js/state.js` — shared mutable app state (`app.entries`, `app.currentMonth`, `app.logSearchQuery`, **`app.analyticsPersonFilter`**, **`app.analyticsLocationFilter`**, …).

`js/render-registry.js` — indirection to avoid import cycles.

`js/scheduled-logic.js` — `scheduledStatus(s)` (overdue / today / soon ≤3 days / later); `intervalLabel`.

`js/utils/date.js` — date helpers and month keys.

`js/api-fetch.js` — fetch wrapper with auth redirect behavior.

`css/chore-tracker-base.css` — reset/theme/shell, top bar, settings dialog, toast.
